::Magmatron::

    "I have new plans for him. You shouldn't have gone, everything was under 
control. But no matter," Magmatron said. "You still need to be Destroned. To 
the lab, that's an order."
    Soon they were in the lab.
    "Maybe I should program you into listening to orders. But I'm not going 
to." Magmatron said. Bobertron was now strapped to the table with triple 
reinforced adamantium (X-Men joke there) straps. There was no way he could 
get up. "This will happen tonight, I am tired of you running around as a 
Predacon, you need to be a Destron, so just sit back and relax."
    Magmatron began the process of changing Bobertron into a Destron. He 
wasn't going let him slip through his fingers again. Soon it was time for 
Magmatron to enter the DNA, but the Megalodon DNA was destroyed in the other 
lab. So he used a DNA from something he found. A hawk. Looking it up in the 
history records it was called a Red Tailed Hawk. He began grafting it onto 
Bobertron. Soon there was nothing left of the Mosesaur and he was all Hawk. 
Now it was time to enter the final stage, Transmetal 2. This time he was 
ready for the surge, it worked completely, his lab was in perfect working 
order and Bobertron was a new bot. He had the ability to cloak for a limited 
period of time and some other nifty features.
